GPL-3.0-or-later is the recommended license for Mujify (strong copyleft keeps
every fork free and open-source, matching the "genuinely free, no paywall" goal).

To finalize: replace THIS file with the full, verbatim GPL-3.0 text from
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt (the license requires the complete text
to accompany distribution). If you prefer a different license, swap this file and
update the "License" section of README.md accordingly.

